name: Dismal Sinkhole Canyon
description:
Introduction

ONLY A COUPLE OF SMALL DROPS. NOT MUCH IN THE WAY OF CANYONEERING MATERIAL.

An additional trip 12-13-14 to check out the upper canyon, and there was not much in the way of technical canyoneering opportunities, but only found a pretty walk-down through the canyon. Also did a 2nd easy option to get into the canyon by hiking up Palmer Canyon to get there.
